הוות מיתצדה
         </quote>
                  <bibl default="false" status="draft">
                     <ref type="witness">79,6</ref>
                     <ref type="witness">II 942: 1</ref>
                  </bibl>
                  <cit type="translation">
                     <quote xml:lang="en">
At the end of this period he [R. Shimʿon] saw a hunter engaged in catching birds. Now whenever he [R. Shimʿon] heard a heavenly voice exclaim from heaven “released!” it escaped; if it exclaimed “death sentence!” it was caught.</quote>
                     <bibl default="false" status="draft">cf. Freedman / Simon II: 730</bibl>
                  </cit>
                  <note>= yShev 9 (38d [209]) (-); bShab 33b (-); PesK be-Shalaḥ 11,16 (-); MKoh 10,8 (<term xml:lang="jpa">ספיקלא</term>); MTeh 17,13 (<term xml:lang="jpa">ספיקלא</term>); MachTeh 17,25 (<term xml:lang="jpa">ספיקלא</term>); EstR 3,7 (<term xml:lang="jpa">ספיקלא</term>); Yalq 133 (42b: 15) (<term xml:lang="jpa">ספקולא</term>)</note>
